strings: <voice_0x01001D09><se_high>Media princess: I haven't seen him play for a long time.
<voice_0x01001D0A><se_high>Media princess: It is lonely and lonely with you and everyone else. in the car going to town
<voice_0x01001D0B><se_high>Media princess: Yes, I'm glad humans and monsters find peace here.
<voice_0x01001D0C><se_high>Media princess: It appears that he has met a friendly monster along the way. But people fear them because they are very rare.
<voice_0x01001D0D><se_high>Media princess: Therefore, there are very few people who do not hold a grudge.
<voice_0x01001D0E><se_high>Media princess: If you don't hide, everybody will be quiet in a good place
